title: Michigan Rally #WhitmerDeathToll | Ep 701
description: Steven Crowder takes the heat to Gov. Gretchen Whitmer at the state Capitol in Michigan and demands that she release the full death count that resulted from her disastrous COVID-19 nursing home policy.
